title: The GRAND SLAM Brothers
body_text:
ECD's "Reunion Era" (2013-present) has undoubtedly featured some of biggest and best contests. The monstrous collision between Sputz & Katz, the titanic struggles between Diana, Melissa, and Lauren, and who could forget the 10 Year Anniversary clash featuring Edwards, Pierce, and Megill, just to name a few.
The Writer hopes that you'll join for ECD's great American bash and, as usual, an event of this magnitude features this monstrous championship encounter over 10 years in the making.
